('64575','22487','5','Panoramic view plot with unique building project in Son Vida'),
('64576','22488','5','This plot of approx. 6,000 m² is situated in a prime location on the highest point of the hill in Son Vida with stunning, unobstructed 360 degree views of the city lights, the bay of Palma, the castle of Bellver and the vast pine groves of the surrounding nature protection areas.\r\nThe approved project with approximately 3,000 m² of net living space plus 1,500 m² of open and covered terraces, 1.000 m² of garage and installations room as well as two large pools impress with a pure minimalist design, generous surfaces and an architecture, which emphasizes the conjunction between spaciousness, harmony of life in nature with the luxury of modern technology. The spacious living area provides space for a total of 15 bedrooms with en suite bathroom, 5 living rooms, kitchens, office, gym, hammam, home cinema, wine cellar and many more.\r\nThis property will be an unique oasis of tranquility, but at the same time located close to the city of Palma and enjoying all the benefits of the urbanization of Son Vida.'),
